            </li>
          </ul>
          <a href="/contact" class="btn btn-primary">Learn More</a>
        </div>
        <div class="glass p-8">
          <div
            class="bg-gradient-to-br from-green/20 to-green-light/20 rounded-lg p-8 text-center"
          >
            <h4 class="text-green mb-4">Transit Revolution</h4>
            <p>
              Powering seamless journeys across India's metro networks with NCMC
